          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The ratio tantalum to titanium nuclei in",
                "the targets was determined from forward-angle, low-",
                "energy triton elastic scattering. The ability to",
                "normalize the results independently within each",
                "spectrum removes errors due to uncertainty in counter",
                "angle, target uniformity and fluctuations in beam-spot",
                "position. As a check on the consistency of the results,",
                "relative angular distributions were obtained by",
                "determining the relative solid angles of the detectors",
                "through measurements of the elastic scattering from",
                "thin gold targets in short runs carried out at regular",
                "intervals during the course of the experiment."
              ]
            }
          ],
